  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If <math alttext=\"x equals 40\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>40</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>, what is the value of <math alttext=\"x plus 6\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>6</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>?</p>",
